{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"d2260e5e21","title":"对徐××同志《关于如何打乒乓球》一文的批示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"f7ca535c4a","index":0,"year":1965,"month":1,"day":12,"articleId":"d2260e5e21"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","name":"毛泽东思想万岁（1961年-1968年）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives3/main/45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"edf92835e7","type":"paragraph","text":"对徐××同志《关于如何打","index":0,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"d2260e5e21"},{"id":"3246228b9b","type":"paragraph","text":"乒乓球》一文的批示","index":1,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"d2260e5e21"},{"id":"be20663ff5","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六五年一月十二日）","index":2,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"d2260e5e21"},{"id":"25030d8496","type":"paragraph","text":"徐××同志的讲话和××同志的批语，印发中央同志们一阅，并希望你们间去后，再加印发，以广宣传。同志们，这是小将们向我们这一大批老将们挑战了，难道我们不应该向他们学习一点什么东西吗？讲话全文充满了辩证唯物论，处处反对唯心主义和任何一种形而上学。多年以来没有看到这样好的作品，他讲的是打球，我们要从他那里学习的是理论、政治、经济、文化、军事。如果我们不向小将们学习，我们就要完蛋了。","index":3,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"d2260e5e21"},{"id":"a1ae097f03","type":"paragraph","text":"中央《关于学习周恩来同志","index":4,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"d2260e5e21"},{"id":"a843b43796","type":"paragraph","text":"政府工作报告的通知》","index":5,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"d2260e5e21"},{"id":"3dc35bf3a5","type":"paragraph","text":"31）","index":6,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"d2260e5e21"},{"id":"97accfae92","type":"paragraph","text":"（摘","index":7,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"d2260e5e21"},{"id":"760ef56e1b","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六五年一月十四日）","index":8,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"d2260e5e21"},{"id":"2e8862b36e","type":"paragraph","text":"外国一切好的经验，好的科学技术，我们都吸收过来，为我们所用。拒绝向外国学习是不对的，当然迷信外国，认为外国的东西都是好的，也是不对的，不论是迷信苏联，还是迷信西方，都不对，正确的态度应当是重科学，破除迷信。","index":9,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"d2260e5e21"},{"id":"9d2eb02de6","type":"paragraph","text":"X","index":10,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"d2260e5e21"},{"id":"c3025c77c4","type":"paragraph","text":"X","index":11,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"d2260e5e21"},{"id":"bd1e419092","type":"paragraph","text":"X","index":12,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"d2260e5e21"},{"id":"dd24fc2156","type":"paragraph","text":"引进新技术不是一味攀仿，照抄照搬。学习外国必须用独创精神，结合超来，引进技术必须同自己钻研结合超来。对于进口的技术装备，必须加以研究，一般从仿制做起，进而结合我国的具体情况加以改进和提高。","index":13,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"d2260e5e21"},{"id":"954288ccc6","type":"paragraph","text":"接见苏班德里约的蓄","index":14,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"d2260e5e21"},{"id":"8638bd549a","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六五年一月二十七日）","index":15,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"d2260e5e21"},{"id":"0feaab9c39","type":"paragraph","text":"好的拿来，坏的丢掉。无论是本国的或外国的都一样，只能批判地接受，不能教条主义，照搬。这样才有希望。","index":16,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"d2260e5e21"},{"id":"ba3a8d6cb0","type":"paragraph","text":"军事学校办得一爆糊涂，正在整理。过去没有军事学校，可好了。打了几十年仗，就是没有军事学校。我们的军队百分之九十以上是不识字和小学程度的。国民党尽办军事学校，什么陆军大学毕业，就是我们这些不识字的兵打倒了它。我们各军区的司合过去都是老粗麻。","index":17,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"d2260e5e21"},{"id":"d67fbfbc9e","type":"paragraph","text":"进军事学校的时间太长了。蒋介石办的黄埔军校，五个月人伍训练，四个月学校毕业。·226·","index":18,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"d2260e5e21"}],"page":{"id":"03d5cc3bb4","publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"d2260e5e21","start":239,"end":239}}}},"__N_SSG":true}